name: Demographer

body:
### Welcome to DemoGrapher
DemoGrapher helps in efficiently visualizing students data segregated by demographics. The information can be refined by numerous powerful filters based on criteria like Student Gender, Ethnicity, Academic Year, Academic Level, College, Department, Major, etc.

### Technology Stack
* Python, Flask, Postgres DB, JavaScript, JQuery, D3, HTML5, Bootstrap.

Please consult the [README](https://github.com/shivam-maharshi/DemoGrapher/blob/master/README.md) for more info.

### Authors and Contributors
Shivam Maharshi (@shivam-maharshi) created this project to contribute to the Virginia Tech Center for Institutional Research in effectively visualizing students demographical data.
